{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"iddb3f37db-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s411"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"411"},"text":"§ 411.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Issuance to reserve banks; nature of obligation; redemption","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Federal reserve notes, to be issued at the discretion of the Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System for the purpose of making advances to Federal reserve banks through the Federal reserve agents as hereinafter set forth and for no other purpose, are authorized. The said notes shall be obligations of the United States and shall be receivable by all national and member banks and Federal reserve banks and for all taxes, customs, and other public dues. They shall be redeemed in lawful money on demand at the Treasury Department of the United States, in the city of Washington, District of Columbia, or at any Federal Reserve bank.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"iddb3f37dc-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1913-12-23/ch6/s16"},"text":"Dec. 23, 1913, ch. 6, § 16","children":[],"tail":" (par.), "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/38/265"},"text":"38 Stat. 265","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1934-01-30/ch6/s2/b/1"},"text":"Jan. 30, 1934, ch. 6, § 2(b)(1)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/48/337"},"text":"48 Stat. 337","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1935-08-23/ch614"},"text":"Aug. 23, 1935, ch. 614","children":[],"tail":", title II, § 203(a), "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/49/704"},"text":"49 Stat. 704","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"iddb3f37dd-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"iddb3f37de-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"iddb3f37df-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Phrase “hereinafter set forth” is from section 16 of the Federal Reserve Act, act ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1913-12-23"},"text":"Dec. 23, 1913","children":[],"tail":". Reference probably means as set forth in sections 17 et seq. of the Federal Reserve Act. For classification of these sections to the Code, see Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"iddb3f37e0-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section is comprised of first par. of section 16 of act ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1913-12-23"},"text":"Dec. 23, 1913","children":[],"tail":". Pars. 2 to 5, 6 (formerly 7), 7 to 10 (formerly 8 to 11, respectively), 12 (formerly 13), 13 (formerly 14), and 14 to 16 (formerly 15, 16, and 18, respectively) of section 16 of act "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1913-12-23"},"text":"Dec. 23, 1913","children":[],"tail":", are classified to sections 412 to 415, 416, 418 to 421, 360, 248–1, and 467, respectively, of this title."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Former pars. 6 and 17 of section 16 of act ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1913-12-23"},"text":"Dec. 23, 1913","children":[],"tail":", formerly classified to sections 415 and 467, respectively, of this title, were repealed by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/90/269"},"text":"Pub. L. 90–269","children":[],"tail":", §§ 5, 7, "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1968-03-18"},"text":"Mar. 18, 1968","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/82/50"},"text":"82 Stat. 50","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Par. 11 (formerly 12) of section 16 of act ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1913-12-23"},"text":"Dec. 23, 1913","children":[],"tail":", formerly classified to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s422"},"text":"section 422 of this title","children":[],"tail":", was superseded by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1934-06-26/ch756/s1/a"},"text":"act June 26, 1934, ch. 756, § 1(a)","children":[],"tail":", (b)(3), "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/48/1225"},"text":"48 Stat. 1225","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"iddb3f37e1-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1934—Act ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1934-01-30"},"text":"Jan. 30, 1934","children":[],"tail":", struck out from last sentence provision permitting redemption in gold."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"iddb3f37e2-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"changeOfName","id":"iddb3f37e3-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Change of Name","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section 203(a) of act ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1935-08-23"},"text":"Aug. 23, 1935","children":[],"tail":", changed name of Federal Reserve Board to Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
